How to run ros2 packages:
cd ~/ros2_ws/
colcon build
ros2 launch bulldozer_control bulldozer.launch.py

NAVIGATION PARAMETER (AUTO NODE)
turn_pwm
drive_pwm
servo_angle
BUCKET_DUMP
BUCKET_CARRY
arrive_tolerance
heading_tolerance
realign_tolerance
obstacle_threshold     

CAR PHYSICAL PARAMETERS (ODOM NODE)
wheel_diameter
wheel_base
ticks_per_rev
max_tick_jump

ESP32 IP PARAMETER (SERIAL NODE)
self.esp32_ip
self.udp_port
